<plot>This entry of RKO's "This is America" series (production number 03-103)tells the story of how a state trooper/highway patrolman is trained and equipped to fight crime. It follows a trooper-recruit with the Connecticut State Police through the details of his training from day-one to his graduation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?604667</url></doc>
